        <content type="html">
            <![CDATA[
                <h2><figure class="post__image"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/TetraPlot160en.png" sizes="(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 768px" srcset="https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/responsive/TetraPlot160en-xs.png 300w ,https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/responsive/TetraPlot160en-sm.png 480w ,https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/responsive/TetraPlot160en-md.png 768w"  alt="Screenshot" width="1332" height="1394"></figure>Overview</h2>
<p>TetraPlot is a tiny program for plotting chemical compositions in 4 component systems on equilateral tetrahedra.</p>
<h2>Download</h2>
<ul>
<li>For Microsoft Windows 7 or later (64 bit), download <a href="https://github.com/n-hatada/tetraplot/releases/download/v1.7.1/TetraPlot1.7.1_Setup.exe">TetraPlot1.7.1_Setup.exe</a> (Released on Jun. 8, 2022.)</li>
<li>The source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/n-hatada/tetraplot">GitHub</a>. You can compile it using <a href="https://www.lazarus-ide.org/">Lazarus</a> for other operating systems.</li>
</ul>
<h2>Installation (on Windows)</h2>
<p>Run the downloaded setup program.</p>
<h2>Usage</h2>
<ol>
<li>Run "TetraPlot" in Start Menu.</li>
<li>Input axis titles at "Axis titles" section.</li>
<li>"Add" a series at "Series list" section and select it.</li>
<li>Edit series information at "Details of the selected series" section.</li>
<li>You will get the tetrahedral diagram on "Diagram" window.</li>
</ol>
<figure class="post__video"><video loading="lazy" width="300" height="150" controls="controls" data-mce-fragment="1">
<source src="TetraPlotMovieEN.mp4" type="video/mp4" /></video></figure>
<h2>Screenshots</h2>
<div class="gallery-wrapper"><div class="gallery"  data-is-empty="false" data-translation="Add images" data-columns="2">
<figure class="gallery__item"><a href="https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/gallery/screenshot01en.PNG" data-size="770x677"><img loading="lazy" src="https://n-hatada.github.io/tetraplot/media/posts/2/gallery/screenshot01en-thumbnail.PNG" alt="" width="720" height="633"></a></figure>
